data.description: This home is gorgeous.  Located close to city park.  Move in ready. Hard wood floors and carpet throughout.  Home has original wood work.  Nice crown molding.  Built ins throughout.  Custom doors with stained glass tops.  Addition to house was added in the 80's which included a master bed room and bath, family room and back set of stairs to the upstairs.  Kitchen has solid counters and stainless appliances.  Third floor room is bedroom but could be an office or play room.  There is a 2 stall detached garage with alley access.  If you wanted to live on Washington Ave this home is for you. Do not let this home pass you by.  Call for a personal viewing today.  Home being sold "AS IS"
